@page "/tutorial"

<PageTitle>Integration Tutorial</PageTitle>

<div class="tutorial-page">
    <h1>Integratie Tutorial</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
        Hoe je <code>&lt;dotnet-grpc-client&gt;</code> en <code>&lt;vuejs-grpc-client&gt;</code>
        kunt gebruiken in je eigen projecten.
    </p>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>1. Vereisten</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>.NET 10 SDK</li>
            <li>De <strong>DrawingService.Grpc</strong> server draaiend op <code>https://localhost:5001</code></li>
            <li>De gepubliceerde <strong>DrawingClient.Wasm</strong> bestanden</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>2. gRPC Server starten</h2>
        <pre><code>cd DrawingService.Grpc
dotnet run</code></pre>
        <p>De server start op <code>https://localhost:5001</code> en biedt gRPC-Web endpoints.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>3. Integratie in een HTML pagina</h2>
        <p>Kopieer de gepubliceerde <code>drawing-client/</code> map naar je webserver en voeg toe:</p>
        <pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Mijn App&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="drawing-client/DrawingClient.Wasm.styles.css" /&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Tekening via gRPC&lt;/h1&gt;

    &lt;dotnet-grpc-client
        service-url="https://mijn-server.nl:5001"
        scene="landschap"
        width="800"
        height="600"&gt;
    &lt;/dotnet-grpc-client&gt;

    &lt;script src="drawing-client/_framework/blazor.webassembly.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>4. HTML Attributen</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Attribuut</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Default</th>
                    <th>Beschrijving</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>service-url</code></td><td>string</td><td><em>(verplicht)</em></td><td>URL van de gRPC server</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>scene</code></td><td>string</td><td><code>landschap</code></td><td>Naam van de scène</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>width</code></td><td>number</td><td><code>800</code></td><td>Canvas breedte (px)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>height</code></td><td>number</td><td><code>600</code></td><td>Canvas hoogte (px)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>auto-play</code></td><td>boolean</td><td><code>true</code></td><td>Automatisch tekenen bij laden</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>5. Scène wisselen via JavaScript</h2>
        <pre><code>// Wijzig de scène dynamisch
const client = document.querySelector('dotnet-grpc-client');
client.setAttribute('scene', 'auto');</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>6. Integratie in Blazor Server</h2>
        <p>Voeg het volgende toe aan je <code>App.razor</code>:</p>
        <pre><code>&lt;!-- In &lt;head&gt; --&gt;
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="drawing-client/DrawingClient.Wasm.styles.css" /&gt;

&lt;!-- Voor &lt;/body&gt; --&gt;
&lt;script src="drawing-client/_framework/blazor.webassembly.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
        <p>Gebruik dan het custom element in elke Razor pagina:</p>
        <pre><code>&lt;dotnet-grpc-client service-url="https://localhost:5001" scene="huis"&gt;
&lt;/dotnet-grpc-client&gt;</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>Vue.js Client: <code>&lt;vuejs-grpc-client&gt;</code></h2>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>7. Integratie in een HTML pagina (Vue)</h2>
        <p>Bouw de Vue client en kopieer <code>vue-drawing-client.js</code> naar je webserver:</p>
        <pre><code>cd drawing-client-vue
npm install
npm run build</code></pre>
        <p>Voeg vervolgens toe aan je HTML pagina:</p>
        <pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Mijn App&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Tekening via gRPC&lt;/h1&gt;

    &lt;vuejs-grpc-client
        service-url="https://mijn-server.nl:5001"
        scene="landschap"
        width="800"
        height="600"&gt;
    &lt;/vuejs-grpc-client&gt;

    &lt;script src="vue-drawing-client.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>8. HTML Attributen (Vue)</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Attribuut</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Default</th>
                    <th>Beschrijving</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>service-url</code></td><td>string</td><td><em>(verplicht)</em></td><td>URL van de gRPC server</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>scene</code></td><td>string</td><td><code>landschap</code></td><td>Naam van de scène</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>width</code></td><td>number</td><td><code>800</code></td><td>Canvas breedte (px)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>height</code></td><td>number</td><td><code>600</code></td><td>Canvas hoogte (px)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>auto-play</code></td><td>boolean</td><td><code>true</code></td><td>Automatisch tekenen bij laden</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>9. Scène wisselen via JavaScript (Vue)</h2>
        <pre><code>const client = document.querySelector('vuejs-grpc-client');
client.setAttribute('scene', 'auto');</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>10. Beide clients op één pagina</h2>
        <p>Omdat beide clients Web Custom Elements zijn, kun je ze naast elkaar gebruiken:</p>
        <pre><code>&lt;dotnet-grpc-client service-url="https://localhost:5001" scene="landschap"&gt;
&lt;/dotnet-grpc-client&gt;

&lt;vuejs-grpc-client service-url="https://localhost:5001" scene="landschap"&gt;
&lt;/vuejs-grpc-client&gt;

&lt;!-- Laad beide runtimes --&gt;
&lt;script src="drawing-client/_framework/blazor.webassembly.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script src="vue-drawing-client.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="tut-section">
        <h2>7. Beschikbare scènes</h2>
        <div class="scene-list">
            <span class="scene-tag">🌳 boom</span>
            <span class="scene-tag">🏠 huis</span>
            <span class="scene-tag">☁️ wolk</span>
            <span class="scene-tag">☀️ zon</span>
            <span class="scene-tag">🚗 auto</span>
            <span class="scene-tag">🏞️ landschap</span>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
